        <prompt>How did the "Crop-Lien Merchant System" affect farmers?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Created a cycle of debt through high-interest credit</option>
            <option letter="b">Provided fair lending practices</option>
            <option letter="c">Improved agricultural profits</option>
            <option letter="d">Supported farmer independence</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Crop-Lien Merchant System created a cycle of debt by providing high-interest credit to farmers who had to pledge future crops as collateral.</explanation>
